Hi there!

About Me

Merhaba! Hello!

I’m Ada, a Freshman Computer Science student at the University of Toronto with a passion for all things tech. When I’m not diving into coding or exploring robotics and AI, you can find me spending time in my favorite hobbies like chess, drawing, and basketball, or simply spending time with my dog (Pako - photos in ).

My love for drawing and creating art mirrors my interest in front-end development, where I enjoy crafting beautiful and functional websites. I also enjoy playing Minecraft, building epic worlds and getting on virtual adventures.

In addition, I am an avid chess player with a rating of 2100+ on Lichess. I have about 25 days of gameplay, however it is not a dedicated time, just a hobby.
